  The  SBI  has  made  it  mandatory  that  the 

minimum balance should be Rs. 5000 in the accounts of the account holders.  This 

is  adversely  affecting  the  people.    It  is  an  injustice  to  them.    The  SBI  should 

immediately withdraw this order.   

 

THE  MINISTER  OF  STATE  IN  THE  MINISTRY  OF  FINANCE 

